Package: masih
Title: Modular Analysis Shiny Interface for Heterogeneity
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Masih", "Sherafatian", 
           email = "masih@alumni.unimelb.edu.au", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1101-1966"))
Description: An interactive R Shiny application for comprehensive single-cell 
    RNA sequencing analysis in cancer research. MASIH provides a user-friendly
    web interface for analyzing single-cell RNA sequencing data to focus on 
    the multidimensional biological portrait of each cancer cell.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
